{
  "openapi": "3.1.0",
  "info": {
    "title": "SAFARI Inference API",
    "description": "Public REST API for wildlife detection model inference.\n\n## Model Types\n\nThe API supports two model types that determine the inference pipeline:\n\n- **detection**: Standard YOLO object detection\n- **classification**: Hybrid SAM3 + YOLOv11-Classify (detect-then-classify)\n\nThe `model_type` is returned in responses so clients can understand which pipeline was used.\n\n## Internal Documentation\n\nFor detailed technical information about routing logic and processing pipelines, see `docs/API_INTERNALS.md`.",
    "version": "1.0.0"
  },
  "paths": {
    "/api/v1/infer/{model_slug}": {
      "post": {
        "tags": [
          "inference"
        ],
        "summary": "Infer Image",
        "description": "Run inference on a single image.\n\n- **model_slug**: Unique identifier for the model (e.g., \"lynx-detector-v2\")\n- **file**: Image file (JPEG, PNG, WebP)\n- **confidence**: Detection/classification confidence threshold (0-1)\n\n**Routing by model_type:**\n- `detection`: Uses YOLO model directly\n- `classification`: Uses SAM3 for detection + YOLOv11-Classify for species ID\n\nReturns predictions with bounding boxes in normalized coordinates (0-1).",
        "operationId": "infer_image_api_v1_infer__model_slug__post",
        "security": [
          {
            "APIKeyHeader": []
          }
        ],
        "parameters": [
          {
            "name": "model_slug",
            "in": "path",
            "required": true,
            "schema": {
              "type": "string",
              "title": "Model Slug"
            }
          },
          {
            "name": "confidence",
            "in": "query",
            "required": false,
            "schema": {
              "type": "number",
              "maximum": 1.0,
              "minimum": 0.0,
              "description": "Confidence threshold for predictions. For hybrid models, this filters classifier output.",
              "default": 0.25,
              "title": "Confidence"
            },
            "description": "Confidence threshold"
          }
        ],
        "requestBody": {
          "required": true,
          "content": {
            "multipart/form-data": {
              "schema": {
                "$ref": "#/components/schemas/Body_infer_image_api_v1_infer__model_slug__post"
              }
            }
          }
        },
        "responses": {
          "200": {
            "description": "Successful Response",
            "content": {
              "application/json": {
                "schema": {
                  "$ref": "#/components/schemas/ImageInferenceResponse"
                }
              }
            }
          },
          "422": {
            "description": "Validation Error",
            "content": {
              "application/json": {
                "schema": {
                  "$ref": "#/components/schemas/HTTPValidationError"
                }
              }
            }
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "/api/v1/infer/{model_slug}/video": {
      "post": {
        "tags": [
          "inference"
        ],
        "summary": "Submit Video Job",
        "description": "Submit a video for async inference processing.\n\n- **model_slug**: Unique identifier for the model\n- **file**: Video file (MP4, MOV, AVI)\n- **confidence**: Detection/classification confidence threshold (0-1)\n- **frame_skip**: Return every Nth frame in results (1 = all frames, 5 = every 5th)\n- **start_time**: Start processing from this time (seconds)\n- **end_time**: Stop processing at this time (seconds)\n\n**Routing by model_type:**\n- `detection`: Uses YOLO with vid_stride (no temporal tracking)\n- `classification`: Uses SAM3VideoSemanticPredictor with full temporal tracking\n\n**Important:** For classification models, SAM3 always processes ALL frames for accurate tracking. The `frame_skip` parameter only filters which frames appear in the output results.\n\nReturns a job_id to poll for progress at /api/v1/jobs/{job_id}",
        "operationId": "submit_video_job_api_v1_infer__model_slug__video_post",
        "security": [
          {
            "APIKeyHeader": []
          }
        ],
        "parameters": [
          {
            "name": "model_slug",
            "in": "path",
            "required": true,
            "schema": {
              "type": "string",
              "title": "Model Slug"
            }
          },
          {
            "name": "confidence",
            "in": "query",
            "required": false,
            "schema": {
              "type": "number",
              "maximum": 1.0,
              "minimum": 0.0,
              "description": "Confidence threshold for predictions",
              "default": 0.25,
              "title": "Confidence"
            },
            "description": "Confidence threshold"
          },
          {
            "name": "frame_skip",
            "in": "query",
            "required": false,
            "schema": {
              "type": "integer",
              "maximum": 30,
              "minimum": 1,
              "description": "Return every Nth frame in results. Note: For classification models using SAM3, all frames are still processed internally for tracking accuracy.",
              "default": 1,
              "title": "Frame Skip"
            },
            "description": "Return every Nth frame in results"
          },
          {
            "name": "start_time",
            "in": "query",
            "required": false,
            "schema": {
              "type": "number",
              "minimum": 0.0,
              "description": "Start time in seconds",
              "default": 0.0,
              "title": "Start Time"
            },
            "description": "Start time in seconds"
          },
          {
            "name": "end_time",
            "in": "query",
            "required": false,
            "schema": {
              "anyOf": [
                {
                  "type": "number",
                  "minimum": 0.0
                },
                {
                  "type": "null"
                }
              ],
              "description": "End time in seconds",
              "title": "End Time"
            },
            "description": "End time in seconds"
          }
        ],
        "requestBody": {
          "required": true,
          "content": {
            "multipart/form-data": {
              "schema": {
                "$ref": "#/components/schemas/Body_submit_video_job_api_v1_infer__model_slug__video_post"
              }
            }
          }
        },
        "responses": {
          "200": {
            "description": "Successful Response",
            "content": {
              "application/json": {
                "schema": {
                  "$ref": "#/components/schemas/VideoJobResponse"
                }
              }
            }
          },
          "422": {
            "description": "Validation Error",
            "content": {
              "application/json": {
                "schema": {
                  "$ref": "#/components/schemas/HTTPValidationError"
                }
              }
            }
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "/api/v1/infer/{model_slug}/batch": {
      "post": {
        "tags": [
          "inference"
        ],
        "summary": "Infer Batch",
        "description": "Run inference on multiple images in a single call.\n\nOptimized for high-throughput frame sequences (e.g., from SAFARIDesktop client). Models are loaded once and reused across all images, eliminating cold start overhead.\n\n- **model_slug**: Unique identifier for the model\n- **files**: Multiple image files (max 100 images, 10MB each)\n- **confidence**: Detection/classification confidence threshold (0-1)\n\n**Routing by model_type:**\n- `detection`: Uses YOLO model directly\n- `classification`: Uses SAM3SemanticPredictor + YOLOv11-Classify\n\nReturns predictions for each image with preserved order.",
        "operationId": "infer_batch_api_v1_infer__model_slug__batch_post",
        "security": [
          {
            "APIKeyHeader": []
          }
        ],
        "parameters": [
          {
            "name": "model_slug",
            "in": "path",
            "required": true,
            "schema": {
              "type": "string",
              "title": "Model Slug"
            }
          },
          {
            "name": "confidence",
            "in": "query",
            "required": false,
            "schema": {
              "type": "number",
              "maximum": 1.0,
              "minimum": 0.0,
              "description": "Confidence threshold for predictions",
              "default": 0.25,
              "title": "Confidence"
            },
            "description": "Confidence threshold"
          }
        ],
        "requestBody": {
          "required": true,
          "content": {
            "multipart/form-data": {
              "schema": {
                "$ref": "#/components/schemas/Body_infer_batch_api_v1_infer__model_slug__batch_post"
              }
            }
          }
        },
        "responses": {
          "200": {
            "description": "Successful Response",
            "content": {
              "application/json": {
                "schema": {
                  "$ref": "#/components/schemas/BatchInferenceResponse"
                }
              }
            }
          },
          "422": {
            "description": "Validation Error",
            "content": {
              "application/json": {
                "schema": {
                  "$ref": "#/components/schemas/HTTPValidationError"
                }
              }
            }
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "/api/v1/jobs/{job_id}": {
      "get": {
        "tags": [
          "jobs"
        ],
        "summary": "Get Job Status",
        "description": "Get the status and progress of an async job.\n\n- **job_id**: The job ID returned from video submission\n\nPoll this endpoint periodically to track progress.\nWhen status is \"completed\", the result field contains predictions.\n\n**Status values:**\n- `pending`: Job queued, not yet started\n- `processing`: Job running, check progress_current/progress_total\n- `completed`: Job finished, result contains predictions\n- `failed`: Job failed, check error_message",
        "operationId": "get_job_status_api_v1_jobs__job_id__get",
        "security": [
          {
            "APIKeyHeader": []
          }
        ],
        "parameters": [
          {
            "name": "job_id",
            "in": "path",
            "required": true,
            "schema": {
              "type": "string",
              "title": "Job Id"
            }
          }
        ],
        "responses": {
          "200": {
            "description": "Successful Response",
            "content": {
              "application/json": {
                "schema": {
                  "$ref": "#/components/schemas/JobStatusResponse"
                }
              }
            }
          },
          "422": {
            "description": "Validation Error",
            "content": {
              "application/json": {
                "schema": {
                  "$ref": "#/components/schemas/HTTPValidationError"
                }
              }
            }
          }
        }
      }
    },
